        <updateDate>2007-09-04T20:00:44Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Independence Prize Act of 2007 - Directs the Secretary of Energy to establish: (1) a program for awarding prizes to U.S. entities for research, development, and commercialization of advanced or transformational technologies for the production, consumption, and distribution of nonpetroleum-based alternative energy and energy efficiency; and (2) an advisory committee.</p> <p></p>]]></text>
      </summary>
